de.gematik.ti.cardreader.provider.api.command

Class AbstractCommandApdu

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.gematik.ti.cardreader.provider.api.command.AbstractApdu
      • de.gematik.ti.cardreader.provider.api.command.AbstractCommandApdu
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommandApdu
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandApdu

    public abstract class AbstractCommandApdu
extends AbstractApdu
implements ICommandApdu

    An APDU Command per ISO/IEC 7816-4. Command APDU encoding options:

    case 1:  |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |                                 len = 4
case 2s: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |LE |                             len = 5
case 3s: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |LC |...BODY...|                  len = 6..260
case 4s: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |LC |...BODY...|LE |              len = 7..261
case 2e: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |00 |LE1|LE2|                     len = 7
case 3e: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |00 |LC1|LC2|...BODY...|          len = 8..65542
case 4e: |CLA|INS|P1 |P2 |00 |LC1|LC2|...BODY...|LE1|LE2|  len =10..65544

LE, LE1, LE2 may be 0x00.
LC must not be 0x00 and LC1|LC2 must not be 0x00|0x00
